{"tid":863070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"種花3年3天全毀 中國網紅粉黛花田被亂踩亂坐...","createTime":"2018-10-15T10:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:14:08.000Z","uid":51183,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"080c92e81da79422b6767eb775b062696ad3cf2b","tid":863070,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:28:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2580550?fbclid=IwAR1tskraD2cwH-19zeQOSAtKJxACKZYfe518AGq1jideAbyz3qoYSmq9NoY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2580550%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1tskraD2cwH-19zeQOSAtKJxACKZYfe518AGq1jideAbyz3qoYSmq9NoY&d=SU4NCEeP1Aeco5ACME9hRACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=d89480e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2580550%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1tskraD2cwH-19zeQOSAtKJxACKZYfe518AGq1jideAbyz3qoYSmq9NoY&h=cba6af97\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2580550?fbclid=IwAR1tskraD2cwH-19zeQOSAtKJxACKZYfe518AGq1jideAbyz3qoYSmq9NoY</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpGQam0Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpGQam0Y.jpg&h=092fe5da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大部分民眾無視花田周圍的圍欄或管理人的制止，直接踩進或躺進花田中進行拍攝，壓倒一大片又一大片原本站立挺直的粉黛草。（圖取自《都市快報》）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國浙江省杭州市濱江江邊公園種有大面積的粉黛亂子草（Muhly grass），日前成為熱門打卡景點，但拍照民眾無視圍欄直接進入花田或踩或坐，讓種了3年的粉黛草，僅3天時間全被毀了。<br />\n<br />\n中國媒體報導，這片粉黛草在10月初盛開，有人把花海照片上傳到網路後，引來一波又一波人潮趕來拍照，大部分民眾無視花田周圍的圍欄或管理人的制止，直接踩進或躺進花田中進行拍攝，壓倒一大片又一大片原本站立挺直的粉黛草。<br />\n<br />\n記者在現場詢問了不少民眾，是否知道不能跨越圍欄進入花田中拍照，大多數人都表示，「不好意思，拍一張就走」。也有少部分人假裝沒聽到，或者答覆了一句，「關你什麼事？」<br />\n<br />\n負責照顧這片花田的鄭姓婦人說，這片粉黛草從澳洲進口，因為一壓就倒、極易長蟲，必須非常小心種植，她和老伴這幾年像「伺候孩子」一樣照顧這片花田，但種了3年的粉黛草，僅3天就被全毀了。<br />\n<br />\n鄭婦哭著說，「我的『孩子』被人欺負，但我無能為力啊...」；她也痛斥，「你們拍照片的人，拍出來的照片很美，可是你們的行為卻很難看」。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php4Vz0RS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php4Vz0RS.jpg&h=58e1e782&s={SIZE}\" />   <br />\n杭州粉黛草在10月初盛開，有人把花海照片上傳到網路後，引來一波又一波人潮趕來拍照。（圖取自《都市快報》）"},{"pid":"415b660b7a6d0c8a1777509b95e52fba89073638","tid":863070,"uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:29:38.000Z","msg":"這就是中国.jpg"},{"pid":"b690c8f452dda7b9e9a87d1069129026e5d9a45e","tid":863070,"uid":166785,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"又贏"},{"pid":"202446fc9761e872f495c098d2d84b669acdf4b3","tid":863070,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"大陸野分分鐘係宣傳來"},{"pid":"d45dc335ac43c02c9aff3c6bb8d602bb3f789f17","tid":863070,"uid":38041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"勵志 台上一分鐘 台下十年功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e083f5a53f72a56873d8a26df6aa9478428f098d","tid":863070,"uid":119330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔怪得中國人去邊度都被人討厭<br />\n有時去旅行<br />\n見到街上有人大聲講大聲笑<br />\n基本上有九成機會對方係中國人<br />\n果D四五十歲既 都仲可以話教育程度不高<br />\n但二三十果班 真係無藉口"},{"pid":"ed82a3980ddb52ecbd8e296dd1118ebfe5bff52e","tid":863070,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:33:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e82e29cae19721a965a0900e9992442fc5aa27","tid":863070,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e083f5a53f72a56873d8a26df6aa9478428f098d","tid":863070,"uid":119330,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔怪得中國人去邊度都被人討厭<br />\n有時去旅行<br />\n見到街上有人大聲講大聲笑<br />\n基本上有九成機會對方係中國人<br />\n果D四五十歲既 都仲可以話教育程度不高<br />\n但二三十果班 真係無藉口"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"關你甚麼事"},